race.description: Inglis Digital Feb Late Sale 19-24 Handicap
race.comment: WEST OF AFRICA (7) proven miler at his top fourth-up. Hard to miss the run when he failed to get a clear crack at them in the straight with an unlucky sixth to King Of Roseau over 1400m in the LR MM Cup at the Gold Coast. Will relish the fast tempo and can finish over the top of these. SUN GOD (16) got out late with an eye catching third over 1600m at this track with the 59.5kg in BM88 class. Massive weight drop today and gets every chance after returning a slick set of figures last start. HELLSING (14) did all the donkey work early and gripped on late with a fighting second over 1600m here. Well weighted with the claim and will be in this for a long way. UNLIMITED (9) kept fresh and back in trip after demolishing an average field over 2100m at Wyong. Kept up to the mark with a recent Rosehill trial over 1000m. Look for him to swoop late. LAVISH EMPIRE (15) caught the eye after making up ground from last on the turn when tenth to King Of Roseau at the Gold Coast.
